Unknown Katana.ability: At the end of your attack, if you wounded the monster, {story_event} Great Divide.

Unknown Sword.ability: The first time you wound with this each Showdown, gain {disorder} [Immortal] and +1d1000 insanity.

Unknown Club.ability: The first time you surpass with this each showdown, the monster is knocked down and ignores Indomitable this round.

Unknown Spear.ability: When you hit with this, draw {hit_location} from the discard pile. Suffer 2 brain damage for each hit. If you need to draw more cards than are discarded, die.

Unknown Whip.ability: When you draw {hit_location} without a critical wound, draw a Unknown Card and add its critical wound effect to this {hit_location}.
